# 🚀 API Integration – JavaScript & Tailwind

## 📌 Overview

This project represents my **first hands-on experience with APIs**.

It is a static webpage where I practiced fetching data from external APIs, rendering it dynamically in the DOM, and styling the interface using Tailwind CSS.

🔗 **Live Demo:**  
https://abdelrahmangalal200101-cpu.github.io/API-Integration---assiment-11/

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5  
- CSS3 (Tailwind CSS)  
- JavaScript (ES6+)  
- Fetch API / AJAX  

---

## 🎯 What I Learned

- How to fetch data from external APIs  
- Rendering dynamic content in the DOM  
- Handling asynchronous data with promises  
- Integrating Tailwind CSS for responsive and clean UI  
- Combining JS logic with styling frameworks for interactive web pages  

---

## 📈 Progress Note

This project marks the beginning of my journey into **dynamic web development**.  

It laid the foundation for **React and full-stack projects**, as it reinforced concepts like:

- Handling data asynchronously  
- Updating UI based on data  
- Structuring code for readability and maintainability  

It represents my transition from static, interactive pages to data-driven applications 🚀
